N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 936.3 - Special conditions

State Regulations

All streams, ponds or other bodies of water which appear
as lines to indicate natural waters on the reference maps herein and which are
not specifically designated in Table I, or all streams or other bodies of water
which are not shown on the reference maps herein, shall be assigned to class
AA-Special, as set forth in Part 702, supra. Notes
